&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of and hands-on experience with distributed systems and cloud services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience developing and debugging system-level software in languages similar to Golang, C++, or Rust (more for Principal).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Computer Science or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to design and build highly reliable, high-performance system software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of leading non-trivial projects from design through production rollout, navigating ambiguity along the way.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of database architecture and operating systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with distributed systems managed via Kubernetes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with one or more major clouds (AWS, Azure, GCP), including cloud networking and identity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with workflow engines, observability stacks (Prometheus, Grafana), and Infrastructure-as-Code (Terraform / Terragrunt).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
